OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPeople 'scared to leave'   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhomes after burning body   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffind                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, People in a Motherwell housing estate  
OL,6, say they are scared to leave their     
OL,7, homes after a man's body was found     
OL,8, burning on a nearby football pitch.    
OL,10,FPolice and firefighters were called to 
OL,11,FMargaret Drive at about 09:00 on       
OL,12,FSaturday after the discovery was made  
OL,13,Fby a member of the public.             
OL,15,FResidents have told the BBC they have  
OL,16,Fbeen "disturbed" by scarce details and 
OL,17,Ffear an attacker could be in the area. 
OL,19,FPolice Scotland has not released       
OL,20,Fdetails on the nature of the incident. 
